### Test API để lấy Current User ID
### Đây là file test cho API GetCurrentUserId và GetCurrentUserInfo

### 1. Test API GetCurrentUserId - Trả về thông tin user hiện tại
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Test/GetCurrentUserId
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 2. Test API GetCurrentUserInfo - Trả về thông tin user hiện tại với context mở rộng
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Test/GetCurrentUserInfo
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 3. Test với localhost khác (nếu port khác)
GET https://localhost:5001/api/Test/GetCurrentUserId
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 4. Test với HTTP (không SSL)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/Test/GetCurrentUserId
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 5. Test với Authentication Header (nếu cần)
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Test/GetCurrentUserId
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 6. Test API GetCurrentUserInfo với Authentication
GET https://localhost:7001/api/Test/GetCurrentUserInfo
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

